# 1. Swagger File Setup

## Location
The original Swagger file (`swagger.yaml`) is stored in the **APIM folder**.  

## Build Integration
During build, the Swagger file is copied into the API project using the `<Content>` directive in the `.csproj`.  
This ensures it is available in the publish output under:

wwwroot\v1\swagger.yaml

r
Копировать код

## Example `.csproj` Configuration
```xml
<ItemGroup>
  <Content Include="..\scripts\APIM\Configuration\Shared\Swagger\swagger.yaml">
    <Link>wwwroot\v1\swagger.yaml</Link>
    <CopyToPublishDirectory>PreserveNewest</CopyToPublishDirectory>
  </Content>
</ItemGroup>